  <p>Buttons and links can now be grouped together so that they appear side-by-side on tablet and desktop by using a <code>&lt;div class="nhsuk-button-group"&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</code> container. If you are currently doing this using custom CSS code, you can remove that code and use the class provided.</p>

